{
  "stem": "945.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we found out-- my family, my grandparents, and my dad-- my family found out the next day that he was taken to Chernovitz, by truck.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They followed him into Chernovitz to find out where he was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did see him, I believe, once.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After that, he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we never heard from him again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- he was-- he had-- his wife was a very sick person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she passed on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he didn't have any children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was just by himself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was my Uncle Moyche.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the first casualty [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that was torn away from our family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That would have been in 1940, in 1940.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So while we lived under this communist system, there were many paradoxes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The communist ideology and systems are very hard to explain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They do things in a way which, to the average person that's brought up in a democratic and free society, is hard to understand.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'll give you an example, for instance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The same Soviets, or the same government that took away people to Siberia and deprived people of their rights of ownership, the same people opened up a Yiddish school-- a Yiddish, I stress, Yiddish school-- that I remember, because I attended that school, had 630-some Yiddish students.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All subjects were taught in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Russian was a language by itself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were taught, one hour, Russian language.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The teachers were all Yiddish, some local.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember, because there's a Josif Burg who still lives in Chernovitz and does extensive writing in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was my Yiddish teacher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And some were Jewish people, Yiddish people, from the Ukraine and from Russia.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
